dispensary.name: Elevate - Edmonton 118th Ave
dispensary.description:
Founded in 2018, Elevate is Edmonton's most trusted and reliable source for cannabis education and information. Elevate 118 was nominated in 2019 for Canada's Top Cannabis Retail Store and is proud to be 100% locally owned and operated! 

Located in the West End of Edmonton right on 118 Avenue, Elevate 118 has been proudly serving Edmontonians since around the time cannabis was legalized! A staple in the Edmonton Cannabis Community, Elevate 118 is there to answer any questions you may have about cannabis and how cannabis could potentially Elevate your lifestyle. 

With something for everyone, Elevate is your best bet for all things cannabis in Edmonton! Come in and see for yourself. Weed love to see you!

products.name: Thrifty Mac N Cookies 1 x 1g Pre Roll
products.description: Thrifty Mac N Cookies Hybrid Pre-Rolls are the gem of a find that you've been looking for with high THC and thrifty prices. Find a smooth orange flavour that is balanced out by floral accents on a sweet, earth finish rolled to perfection in these Hybrid Pre-Rolls.

products.name: WINK Tangerine Cookies
products.description: This mouth-watering hybrid is crossed with tangie and thin mint GSC. These rock-hard buds are caked in gooey crystals and fill the room with the aroma of orange cream soda.

products.name: Pure Sunfarms Baked Animal
products.description: Baked Animal is a BC-grown cultivar from the Pure Sunfarms greenhouse. This potent hybrid is a cross of the widely popular Animal Face and smooth-smoking Baker's Delight. Featuring sweet aromas of berries, cake, cream and light gas from dominant terpenes myrcene, caryophyllene and limonene. Its dense and colourful buds are rich with sugary trichomes. Pure BC bud, hand-harvested, hang-dried and hand-finished.

products.name: Redecan Space Age Cake
products.description: Galactic heights await with Space Age Cake. A profoundly potent, indulgent indica offering creamy pepper, citrus and nutty flavours. This GSC x Snow Lotus cross is everything you love about cookies strains with an unexpectedly bright fruit and berry aromatic backbone from the caryophyllene, limonene and linalool dominant terps.

products.name: San Rafael Electric Honeydew
products.description: Electric Honeydew by San Rafael '71 is a premium, high-THC hybrid strain with unique genetics, bred from GSC x 91 OG Krypt Melon. Electric Honeydew's flavour profile features strong notes of gas, melon, and pine. The flower is characterized by dense, dark green buds with flashes of bright orange pistils. Cultivated under the highest quality standards, all of our premium dried flower is hang-dried, and carefully finished and bottled by hand. Each jar includes a humidity packet for freshness.

products.name: Pedro's Sweet Sativa
products.description: ***Dominican Sativa with White Russian and an unknown Indica*** (Beta-caryophyllene, Alpha-pinene, Beta-pinene) smells sweet with undertones of spice. Bred here in Canada, this sativa-dominant hybrid is high in THC with a unique terpene profile and large, airy flowers.

products.name: Space Race Cannabis Event Horizon
products.description: Step into the gravitational pull of Event Horizon, the Hybrid 3.5g dried flower that unveils the mysteries of the universe. Immerse yourself in a cosmic experience as you explore the flavors and aromas of this meticulously cultivated strain. Journey beyond the boundaries of ordinary consciousness and enter a realm where relaxation and inspiration merge. Let Event Horizon be your guide as you venture into the abyss, embracing the cosmic energy that awaits within each bud.

products.name: Tribal Cuban Linx 3.5g
products.description: Cuban Linx is a Sativa-dominant strain of cannabis. TK Skunk x Trigerian, Breeder Swamp Boys Seeds. With its refreshing lemon-gas a\roma and diverse terpenes profile, this genetic typically hits 23 - 29 percent THC and routinely hits over 4 percent terpenes. Expect prominent lemon gas pine flavours from inhale to exhale, and a white ash when consuming. The strain is very comparable to the legendary Super Lemon Haze.

products.name: San Rafael Black Jelly
products.description: Black Jelly by San Rafael '71 is a premium, indoor-grown strain developed from Alien Cake 3030 genetics. What makes this sativa so special is its one-of-a-kind aroma of licorice and anise with hidden notes of sweet fruit. Its dense buds come impressive in size and shape with eye-catching green and orange hues, topped with a coat of sparkling trichomes. Black Jelly is hang-dried, hand-finished, and carefully hand-bottled with an included humidity pack.

products.name: Freedom Cannabis (SATIVA) Reserve
products.description: Freedom Cannabis' Freedom Reserve is high THC, craft quality cannabis which will be a rotating strain seasonally based. This sativa dominant strain (Freedom's Luminate Product Line) will only feature ultra-manicured buds. Freedom's flower is packaged in an old school 'Tuna Can' fully recyclable tin packaging for guaranteed freshness.

products.name: San Rafael Ponderosa Pine
products.description: Ponderosa Pine is a premium, indoor-grown flower that was bred from exclusive, top-tier genetics. A high-THC sativa, Ponderosa Pine hits with a medley of dough, pine, and diesel notes. Ponderosa Pine's eye-catching buds display a vibrant palette of royal green and bright violet hues and blanketed in frosty trichomes for an unforgettable first impression. Ponderosa Pine is hang-dried, hand-finished, and carefully hand-bottled with an included humidity pack.

products.name: San Rafael Cosmic Cream
products.description: Cosmic Cream by San Rafael '71 is an impressively high-THC indica bred from original, elite genetics developed by our R&D team at Occo - a world-renowned breeding facility nestled in Comox, BC. This top-tier indica takes you on a nostalgic trip with its comforting aroma, reminiscent of sweet cereal milk with subtle hints of fruit and loamy earth. Dank and dense, Cosmic Cream's flowers are compact and acorn-shaped with a glistening sheen of visible trichomes. Cosmic Cream is hang-dried, hand-finished, and carefully hand-bottled with an included humidity pack.
products.strainDescription: Cream is a hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Wedding Cake and Gelato #33. Cream is 14% THC, making this strain an ideal choice for beginner cannabis consumers. Leafly customers tell us Cream effects include feeling focused,  aroused, and tingly. Medical marijuana patients often choose Cream when dealing with symptoms associated with muscle spasms, pain, and depression. Bred by Cream Crop Co, Cream features flavors like flowery, berry, and pungent. The dominant terpene of this strain is Myrcene. The average price of Cream typically ranges from $30-$40. If you’ve smoked, dabbed, or consumed Cream, tell us about your experience by leaving a strain review.

products.name: San Rafael Moon Berry
products.description: Moon Berry by San Rafael '71 is a premium and balanced cultivar bred from popular medical strains, Vespera and Equiposa genetics. With an even 1:1 ratio of THC to CBD, Moon Berry is perfect for those seeking a full flavour experience with more moderate THC and balanced CBD levels. This hybrid strain's terpene profile features pleasing aroma notes of berries, cream, and lemon coming off stunning, frosty green flowers. Moon Berry is cultivated under the highest quality standards using hang-drying, hand-finishing, and hand-bottling for an excellent finished product. Every jar includes a humidity packet to ensure maximum freshness.
products.strainDescription: Moon Berry is an indica-dominant hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Gelato 33, Gelato 41, and Gelato 42. This strain is 25% sativa and 75% indica. Moon Berry is a rare and potent strain that was bred by Arete Hemp, a family-owned and operated company that is purpose-driven with the sole intentions of helping others. This strain is known for its scents of sweet berry and gas with a creamy undertone. Moon Berry is 19.2% THCa, making this strain an ideal choice for cannabis consumers who enjoy relaxing and soothing effects. Moon Berry is a type 1 hemp flower grown indoors in a coco medium. It is not widely available in the market. If you’ve smoked, dabbed, or consumed Moon Berry, tell us about your experience by leaving a strain review.

products.name: Spinach Peach Gelato
products.description: Grab a scoop, roll it up or put it in a bowl. Spinach Peach Gelato dried flower and pre-rolls bring flavours of sweet, juicy peach and creamy gelato thanks to lineage tracing back to Cake Creashers X Marionberry. With terpenes like myrcene, limonene, and linalool, you'll feel like you've got a double-decker gelato sundae with peaches on top. It's easy to melt away with this high potency strain.
products.strainDescription: Like the fruit it is named for, Marionberry Kush is a delicious hybrid bred by Heroes of the Farm. A well-balanced cross of Raspberry Kush and Space Queen that puts off a full spectrum of fruity flavors, Marionberry Kush closely resembles her genetic “sister” Cinderella 99. There are six main phenotypes of Marionberry that all show a range of fruit flavors like passionfruit and raspberry. The aroma is smooth, sweet, and earthy with a sour twist. The effects are pronounced and uplift the mind almost immediately and then slowly relax the body without putting you to sleep.

products.name: Muskoka Grown Sugar Cookies
products.description: A High THC Indica-leaning hybrid with an aroma of fuel, rubber & grapefruit. Dense buds, covered in trichomes. Hang Dried. Well Cured.
products.strainDescription: Pink Cookies, also known as Wedding Cake, is the familial genetic cross of Girl Scout Cookies and Cherry Pie. This delectable treat is rich with tangy sweet earth and pepper, taking notes and dimension from its OG and Durban Poison parentage.

products.name: Reef Organic Queen SanG 3.5g
products.description: Reminiscent of a summer fruit salad with sharp orange and lemon scents backed with a soft creamy undertone, Queen SanG fills the room with a delightfully fresh bouquet that invigorates your senses.

products.name: GreenSeal Pink Octane
products.description: Pink Octane's sky-high THC and gassy undertones shot it straight to the top of GreenSeal's in-house Nursery program. Absolutely covered with frosty trichomes, the visible potency of this blushing indica-typical phenotype is confirmed by its powerfully euphoric and relaxing effects. You'll be tickled pink by its sweet and nutty flavour profile, mingled with a subtle touch of funky fuel aroma.

products.name: Muskoka Grown Berry Smasher
products.description: Bold fruit flavour from Blueberry backed by the potency of Original Glue. Berry Smasher provides a satisfying smoke at an affordable price.
products.strainDescription: Glueberry is an evenly-balanced hybrid marijuana strain made by crossing Blueberry with Gorilla Glue and OG Kush. This triple threat of a strain can pack a heavy punch of effects that will make you feel euphoric before lulling you into a chilled out state. Glueberry has a fruity, blueberry flavor profile with bright hints of citrus. Medical marijuana patients choose this strain to help fight symptoms related to PTSD and chronic anxiety.

products.name: Space Race Cannabis Event Horizon
products.description: Step into the gravitational pull of Event Horizon, the Hybrid 3.5g dried flower that unveils the mysteries of the universe. Journey beyond the boundaries of ordinary consciousness and enter a realm where relaxation and inspiration merge. Let Event Horizon be your guide as you venture into the abyss, embracing the cosmic energy that awaits within each bud.

Ponderosa Pine is hang-dried, hand-finished, and carefully hand-bottled with an included humidity pack.

products.name: San Rafael Cosmic Cream

Cosmic Cream is hang-dried, hand-finished, and carefully hand-bottled with an included humidity pack.

products.name: San Rafael Moon Berry
products.description: Moon Berry by San Rafael '71 is a premium and balanced cultivar bred from popular medical strains, Vespera and Equiposa genetics. This hybrid strain's terpene profile features pleasing aroma notes of berries, cream, and lemon coming off stunning, frosty green flowers. Moon Berry is cultivated under the highest quality standards using hang-drying, hand-finishing, and hand-bottling for an excellent finished product. Every jar includes a humidity packet to ensure maximum freshness.
products.strainDescription: Moon Berry is an indica-dominant hybrid weed strain made from a genetic cross between Gelato 33, Gelato 41, and Gelato 42. This strain is 25% sativa and 75% indica. Moon Berry is a rare and potent strain that was bred by Arete Hemp, a family-owned and operated company that is purpose-driven with the sole intentions of helping others. This strain is known for its scents of sweet berry and gas with a creamy undertone. Moon Berry is 19.2% THCa, making this strain an ideal choice for cannabis consumers who enjoy relaxing and soothing effects. Moon Berry is a type 1 hemp flower grown indoors in a coco medium. It is not widely available in the market. If you’ve smoked, dabbed, or consumed Moon Berry, tell us about your experience by leaving a strain review.

products.name: Spinach Peach Gelato
products.description: Grab a scoop, roll it up or put it in a bowl. Spinach Peach Gelato dried flower and pre-rolls bring flavours of sweet, juicy peach and creamy gelato thanks to lineage tracing back to Cake Creashers X Marionberry. With terpenes like myrcene, limonene, and linalool, you'll feel like you've got a double-decker gelato sundae with peaches on top. It's easy to melt away with this high potency strain.
products.strainDescription: Like the fruit it is named for, Marionberry Kush is a delicious hybrid bred by Heroes of the Farm. A well-balanced cross of Raspberry Kush and Space Queen that puts off a full spectrum of fruity flavors, Marionberry Kush closely resembles her genetic “sister” Cinderella 99. There are six main phenotypes of Marionberry that all show a range of fruit flavors like passionfruit and raspberry. The aroma is smooth, sweet, and earthy with a sour twist. The effects are pronounced and uplift the mind almost immediately and then slowly relax the body without putting you to sleep.

products.name: Muskoka Grown Sugar Cookies
products.description: A High THC Indica-leaning hybrid with an aroma of fuel, rubber & grapefruit. Dense buds, covered in trichomes. Hang Dried. Well Cured.

products.name: Reef Organic Queen SanG 3.5g
products.description: Reminiscent of a summer fruit salad with sharp orange and lemon scents backed with a soft creamy undertone, Queen SanG fills the room with a delightfully fresh bouquet that invigorates your senses.

products.name: GreenSeal Pink Octane

Absolutely covered with frosty trichomes, the visible potency of this blushing indica-typical phenotype is confirmed by its powerfully euphoric and relaxing effects. You'll be tickled pink by its sweet and nutty flavour profile, mingled with a subtle touch of funky fuel aroma.

products.name: Muskoka Grown Berry Smasher
products.description: Bold fruit flavour from Blueberry backed by the potency of Original Glue. Berry Smasher provides a satisfying smoke at an affordable price.

Glueberry has a fruity, blueberry flavor profile with bright hints of citrus. Medical marijuana patients choose this strain to help fight symptoms related to PTSD and chronic anxiety.

products.name: Thrifty Mac N Cookies 1 x 1g Pre Roll
products.description: Thrifty Mac N Cookies Hybrid Pre-Rolls are the gem of a find that you've been looking for with high THC and thrifty prices. Find a smooth orange flavour that is balanced out by floral accents on a sweet, earth finish rolled to perfection in these Hybrid Pre-Rolls.

products.name: WINK Tangerine Cookies
products.description: This mouth-watering hybrid is crossed with tangie and thin mint GSC. These rock-hard buds are caked in gooey crystals and fill the room with the aroma of orange cream soda.

products.name: Pure Sunfarms Baked Animal

Featuring sweet aromas of berries, cake, cream and light gas from dominant terpenes myrcene, caryophyllene and limonene. Its dense and colourful buds are rich with sugary trichomes. Pure BC bud, hand-harvested, hang-dried and hand-finished.

products.name: Redecan Space Age Cake
